# Contact Form System

## Overview
Complete contact form system with admin management, validation, and email notifications.

## Core Files
- **Template**: [themes/aratavietnam/page-templates/contact.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/page-templates/contact.php) - Contact page template
- **Form Handler**: [themes/aratavietnam/inc/contact-form.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/inc/contact-form.php) - Form processing and admin
- **Meta Fields**: [themes/aratavietnam/inc/contact-meta.php](mdc:themes/aratavietnam/inc/contact-meta.php) - Editable contact info

## Form Fields
- **Họ và tên** (required) - Minimum 2 characters
- **Email** (required) - Valid email format
- **Số điện thoại** (optional) - Vietnamese phone format
- **Chủ đề** (optional) - Subject line
- **Nội dung** (required) - Minimum 10 characters

## Validation Rules
```javascript
// Client-side validation
- Name: min 2 characters
- Email: valid email format
- Phone: optional, Vietnamese format
- Message: min 10 characters
```

## Security Features
- **Nonce Verification**: CSRF protection
- **Honeypot Field**: Spam prevention
- **Input Sanitization**: Data cleaning
- **Server-side Validation**: Double-check client validation

## Admin Interface
- **Custom Post Type**: `contact_submission`
- **Admin Columns**: Name, Email, Phone, Date
- **Detail View**: Full submission details
- **Email Notifications**: Automatic admin alerts

## Database Structure
```sql
wp_posts (contact_submission)
├── post_title: "Contact from [Name] ([Email])"
└── wp_postmeta:
    ├── arata_name: Contact name
    ├── arata_email: Contact email
    ├── arata_phone: Contact phone
    ├── arata_subject: Subject line
    └── arata_message: Message content
```

## Usage
1. Create page with "Contact Page" template
2. Configure contact info in page meta fields
3. Form automatically handles submissions
4. View submissions in WordPress admin under "Liên hệ"
